  "terms_title": "Term & Conditions",
  "terms_section1_title": "1. Welcome!",
  "terms_section1_body": "Nmimes is a fun app to help you learn and practice math. By using this app, you agree to follow these simple rules.",
  "terms_section2_title": "2. Who Can Use the App?",
  "terms_section2_body": "This app is for students aged 13 and above.\nIf you are under 18, a parent or guardian should know you are using the app.",
  "terms_section3_title": "3. Your Account",
  "terms_section3_body": "Use your real and correct information.\nKeep your login details safe.\nDon't share your account with others.",
  "terms_section4_title": "4. How to Use Nmimes",
  "terms_section4_body": "You can use the app to:\n• Learn math\n• Ask AI for help\n• Join study rooms\n• Play friendly challenges\n\nPlease don't:\n• Be rude or mean to others\n• Share bad or unsafe messages\n• Try to break or misuse the app",
  "terms_section5_title": "5. About AI Help",
  "terms_section5_body": "AI helps explain math in an easy way.\nSometimes AI can make mistakes.\nUse AI to learn, not just to copy answers.",
  "terms_section6_title": "6. Study Rooms & Challenges",
  "terms_section6_body": "Be kind and respectful in study rooms.\nChallenges are just for fun and learning.\nPlay fair and support your friends.",
  "terms_section7_title": "7. Rewards & Points",
  "terms_section7_body": "Points, badges, and rewards are for motivation.\nThey are not school grades.",
  "terms_section8_title": "8. Parent Mode",
  "terms_section8_body": "Parents can check activity and control settings.\nDon't try to change parent controls without permission.",
  "terms_section9_title": "9. Your Privacy",
  "terms_section9_body": "We keep your information safe.\nWe do not sell your personal data.\nMore details are in our Privacy Policy.",
  "terms_section10_title": "10. Notifications",
  "terms_section10_body": "You may get reminders and updates.\nYou can turn notifications on or off in settings.",
  "terms_section11_title": "11. Following the Rules",
  "terms_section11_body": "If rules are broken, your account may be paused or closed.\nYou can delete your account anytime from settings.",
  "terms_section12_title": "12. App Content",
  "terms_section12_body": "Everything in Nmimes belongs to the app.\nDon't copy or share it without permission.",
  "terms_section13_title": "13. Need Help?",
  "terms_section13_body": "Use the In-App Support Chat if you need help or have questions.",
  "terms_section14_title": "14. Changes",
  "terms_section14_body": "Rules may change sometimes.\nKeep using the app means you agree to the new rules.",
  "terms_finalMessage": "👍 Final Message for Kids\nBe kind. Learn well. Have fun with math! 🎉",

  "privacy_title": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacy_section1_title": "1. Welcome",
  "privacy_section1_body": "We respect your privacy. This page explains what information we collect and how we use it.",
  "privacy_section2_title": "2. What Information We Collect",
  "privacy_section2_body": "We may collect:\n\n✔ Account Information\n• Name or nickname\n• Email or phone number\n• Profile picture (avatar)\n\n✔ Learning Information\n• Your progress\n• Points and badges\n• Challenges completed\n• Topics you study\n\n✔ Device Information\n• Device type (phone/tablet)\n• App version",
  "privacy_section3_title": "3. Why We Collect This Information",
  "privacy_section3_body": "We use this information to:\n• Help you learn better\n• Save your progress\n• Improve the app\n• Show your points and badges\n• Provide support if you need help",
  "privacy_section4_title": "4. Do We Share Your Information?",
  "privacy_section4_body": "No, we do not sell your information.\n\nWe may share data only in these cases:\n• If the law requires it\n• To protect users from harm\n• To keep the app safe",
  "privacy_section5_title": "5. Parents & Safety",
  "privacy_section5_body": "Parents can use Parent Mode to view learning progress.\nStudents should not share personal details with strangers.",
  "privacy_section6_title": "6. Study Rooms",
  "privacy_section6_body": "Study rooms are for friendly learning.\nPlease don't share personal information in chat rooms.",
  "privacy_section7_title": "7. Cookies & Tracking",
  "privacy_section7_body": "We may use small tools to improve the app (like performance tracking). These tools do not collect personal data like your name or email.",
  "privacy_section8_title": "8. Your Rights",
  "privacy_section8_body": "You can:\n• Ask us to delete your account\n• Ask us what data we have\n• Request changes to your information",
  "privacy_section9_title": "9. Security",
  "privacy_section9_body": "We use strong security to protect your data. But please remember:\n• Keep your password safe\n• Don't share your account",
  "privacy_section10_title": "10. Changes to This Policy",
  "privacy_section10_body": "We may update this policy sometimes. If we do, we will let you know in the app.",
  "privacy_section11_title": "11. Contact",
  "privacy_section11_body": "If you have questions, you can contact us through In-App Support Chat.",
  "privacy_finalMessage": "Final Message\nWe are committed to keeping your information safe and secure.",

